title: Apartments in the heart of Uptown! Fantastic walking score
posting_body: ['The 101 John Apartments is located in an AMAZING location just steps from the newly built Climate Pledge Arena!', 'From here, you can walk to Kerry Park and enjoy the best views of the city.', 'In addition, you will find Metropolitan Market, Bartells, CVS pharmacy, Safeway, and many other stores.', 'We are also in close proximity to public transportation along with many coffee shops, bars, restaurants, etc.', 'KEY FEATURES', '• SIZE: 1,248 square feet', '• AVAILABLE: August', '• LEASE LENGTH: Flexible lease terms', '• LAUNDRY:', 'In the unit', '• UTILITIES: water/sewer/garbage for one occupant $100 and $50 for each additional occupant', '• PETS: Cats and dogs under 40 pounds are allowed ($300 pet deposit and $50 pet rent)', '• CONTROLLED ACCESS:', 'Yes', 'RENTAL FEATURES', '• Stainless steel refrigerator', '• Stainless steel dishwasher', '• Stainless steel Stove/oven', '• Beautiful vinyl plank flooring', '• Open layout', '• Beautiful cabinets and counter tops', '• Luxurious finishes in the bathrooms', '• Lots of bright and natural light', '• Washer / dryer IN the unit', '• And much more!', 'COMMUNITY FEATURES', '• Controlled access', '• Amazing views of the city and Elliott Bay', '• Near public transportation', '• Bike rack', '• Non-smoking', '• Elevator', 'FINANCIALS', '• $42.00 application fee', '• $600.00 Security deposit', 'Photos/video are of a unit with the same floor plan.', 'Will update with photos of unit when available.']
